thread.title: BRIEF-Pfenex And NT Pharma Enter Into A Development And License Agreement For Pfenex's PF708 Therapeutic Equivalent Candidate To Forteo

title: BRIEF-Pfenex And NT Pharma Enter Into A Development And License Agreement For Pfenex's PF708 Therapeutic Equivalent Candidate To Forteo

organizations.name: pf708 therapeutic equivalent candidate to forteo reuters
reuters) - china nt pharma group co ltd

text:
April 18 (Reuters) - China NT Pharma Group Co Ltd:
* PFENEX AND NT PHARMA ENTER INTO A DEVELOPMENT AND LICENSE AGREEMENT FOR PFENEX’S PF708 THERAPEUTIC EQUIVALENT CANDIDATE TO FORTEO®
* PFENEX INC - PFENEX RECEIVED A PAYMENT OF $2.5 MILLION UPON SIGNING OF AGREEMENT
* PFENEX INC - PFENEX MAY BE ELIGIBLE TO RECEIVE ADDITIONAL PAYMENTS OF UP TO $22.5 MILLION BASED ON ACHIEVEMENT OF DEVELOPMENT, SALES-RELATED MILESTONES
* PFENEX INC - PFENEX MAY ALSO BE ELIGIBLE TO RECEIVE DOUBLE-DIGIT ROYALTIES ON NET PRODUCT SALES Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
